                     <summary>Very big angel, probably Archangel Gabriel, almost naked, he has only a cloth fixed by a strip around his chest and going down the lower part of his body, more to his left side. He has got big wings coming out of his back and a long trumpet (??) in his left hand. Large statue of a male angel, with his right hand semi-flexe upwards and his left by his side holding a trumpet. Very classical style. There is a palm branch by his foot.</summary>
